run1.title: Morning run with Trish
run1.description: Nice little morning run with Trish. We went up to where our apartment will be when we move in a few weeks from now. We then jumped right up to pipe from Mount Ogden golf course. There was a decent amount of elevation gain, but it wasn't too bad. We enjoyed the downhill on the way back.

run2.title: Mile repeats for regionals
run2.description: I probably went a little harder than I should've. The chances that I make regionals are unfortunately pretty low, but I still have a chance. It was nice to get out here and just run really hard. Coach wanted us to step it down a little slower than we did, and after that 3rd one he told us not to go much faster. Running fast is fun though. Hopefully I get in.
